snippet.title: Dustin Adair's "Poker With Bob"  -  Awesome game for iPhone/iPad/iPod!! Voice by Ed Mace
snippet.description:
This game blows away all competition!! Wish I could elaborate but there is SOOOO much more to this game than meets the eye-trust me on this!! You simply just have to get it! Over 2 years in the making from master animator Dustin Adair whose work can be seen on Fringe, V, Battlestar Galactica, No Ordinary Family, Terminator: Sarah Connor Chronicles, Transformers: War for Cybertron, and Halo 3.Enough said.
DISCLAIMER:I do not own this film/video. I merely recorded the voice of Bob.
http://edmace.com/
